          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The total number of projectiles corresponding to each",
                "spectrum was obtained with the help of a calibrated",
                "current integrator connected to an aligned Faraday cup",
                "with electron suppression. The beam direction was",
                "monitored continuously."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The thin (17.8+-0.3 mu-g/cm2) 99Ru target.",
                "This 99Ru film was prepared by electron bombardment",
                "evaporation of metallic 99Ru powder, isotopically",
                "enriched to 97.6%, onto a thin carbon backing."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PLATE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The tritons produced in the reaction were",
                "momentum analyzed by the Enge magnetic spectrograph",
                "and detected in nuclear emulsion (Fuji G6B, 50 mu-m",
                "thick). Spectra were taken at eight judiciously",
                "chosen scattering angles, from 58. to 40. degr. After",
                "processing, the exposed emulsion was scanned in strips",
                "of 200 mu-m across the plates."
              ]
            }
          ],
